I'm sorry.

44:29.360 --> 44:30.660
I'm just...

44:34.060 --> 44:35.240
I know these
things are scary,

44:35.440 --> 44:38.940
and... I know that
these aren't things

44:39.140 --> 44:42.730
that you really
want to talk about, but...

44:42.930 --> 44:45.680
I am at
the end of my rope.

44:48.120 --> 44:49.070
Please.

44:53.290 --> 44:54.820
Everyone died.

44:57.080 --> 44:59.400
When Christopher started
seeing that symbol,

44:59.600 --> 45:02.140
things... changed.

45:02.340 --> 45:03.360
He changed,

45:03.560 --> 45:05.660
and he didn't make
people laugh anymore.

45:05.860 --> 45:08.220
He-- he stopped
smiling.

45:09.350 --> 45:11.890
One night, my mother told me
to hide somewhere new,

45:12.090 --> 45:14.150
somewhere different, somewhere
Christopher didn't know,

45:14.350 --> 45:16.930
and when I woke up
the next morning, everyone...

45:22.980 --> 45:24.060
[moans quietly]

45:25.370 --> 45:27.730
There are
bad things here.

45:27.930 --> 45:30.200
They make people
do bad things.

45:31.250 --> 45:32.250
I'm sorry.

