[child 1] Anghkooey!

46:26.300 --> 46:27.780
[child 2] Anghkooey!

46:31.130 --> 46:32.790
[child 3] Anghkooey.

46:32.990 --> 46:34.840
[child 4] Anghkooey.

46:35.040 --> 46:36.230
[child 1] Anghkooey!

46:36.430 --> 46:37.800
[child 2] Anghkooey!

46:38.000 --> 46:40.800
[child 3] Anghkooey!

46:41.000 --> 46:41.930
[child 4] Anghkooey!

46:42.130 --> 46:43.460
[child 1] Anghkooey.

46:43.660 --> 46:48.420
[children repeating] Anghkooey.
Anghkooey. Anghkooey.

46:48.620 --> 46:49.770
- Who are you?
- Anghkooey.

46:49.970 --> 46:51.380
- Anghkooey.
- Anghkooey.

46:51.580 --> 46:54.380
- [children] Anghkooey.
- I'm not afraid of you.

46:54.580 --> 46:56.380
- [children] Anghkooey.
- I'm not afraid of you.

46:56.580 --> 46:59.040
[children] Anghkooey, Anghkooey,
Anghkooey, Anghkooey!

46:59.240 --> 47:02.210
No, no, no, no, no, no, no, no,
no, no, no, no, no, no, no!

47:02.410 --> 47:04.390
Don't touch me! Don't touch me!
Don't! Don't! Don't, please!

47:04.590 --> 47:07.520
Don't, don't, don't, don't,
don't, don't, don't!

47:07.720 --> 47:09.220
Don't touch me! Don't touch me!
Don't touch me!

47:09.420 --> 47:11.050
- Don't touch me, please!
- [children] Anghkooey!

47:11.250 --> 47:13.310
- Please don't touch me!
- [children] Anghkooey!

47:13.510 --> 47:16.450
No, no, no! Don't touch me!
Don't touch me!

47:16.650 --> 47:18.800
[children] Anghkooey, Anghkooey,
Anghkooey, Anghkooey.

47:19.000 --> 47:20.280
No! Don't! No! No!

47:20.480 --> 47:22.970
Don't touch me! Please don't
touch me! Don't touch me!

47:23.170 --> 47:25.100
Don't touch me! [pants]

47:27.540 --> 47:29.810
Huh? I don't--

47:30.010 --> 47:31.020
[Jade] Hey! Hey!

47:32.190 --> 47:33.890
- You okay?
- [Tabitha] I don't...

47:34.980 --> 47:36.110
Did you see that?

47:38.460 --> 47:40.380
Your nose is-- your
nose is bleeding.

47:40.580 --> 47:43.380
Did you see that? Did you see
them? Where the fuck...

47:45.340 --> 47:46.470
See? See what?

47:47.690 --> 47:48.910
See who?

47:49.110 --> 47:51.260
[breathing heavily]

47:51.460 --> 47:52.340
What?

