back to World War II.

49:09.280 --> 49:10.910
Look. We don't have to
trust each other.

49:11.110 --> 49:12.300
We don't even have to
like each other.

49:12.500 --> 49:14.380
But we've gotta start
working together on this.

49:17.560 --> 49:19.400
Now, I don't know what
they want from us,

49:19.590 --> 49:21.480
