a more rational explanation

49:21.680 --> 49:24.040
for what's going on here,
I'd love to hear it.

49:29.530 --> 49:30.570
I gotta go, Jim.

49:35.790 --> 49:38.140
[grunting]

49:42.450 --> 49:43.670
Hello?

